title: Ski jumping at the 2012 Winter Youth Olympics – Girls' individual
text:
The girls' individual competition of the <a href="ski%20jumping">ski jumping</a> events at the <a href="2012%20Winter%20Youth%20Olympics">2012 Winter Youth Olympics</a> in <a href="Innsbruck">Innsbruck</a>, <a href="Austria">Austria</a>, was held on January 14, at the <a href="Toni-Seelos-Olympiaschanze">Toni-Seelos-Olympiaschanze</a>. 14 athletes from 14 different countries took part in this event.
Results.
The first round was started on 14 January at 11:00 and the final round at 12:00.
